What is the positive square root of the product $10 \times 15 \times 24$? ||| \begin{align*}
\sqrt{10 \cdot 15 \cdot 24} &= \sqrt{(2 \cdot 5) \cdot (3 \cdot 5) \cdot (2 \cdot 3 \cdot 4)} \\
&= \sqrt{2^2 \cdot 5^2 \cdot (2 \cdot 4)} \\
&= 2 \cdot 5 \cdot 4 \\
&= \boxed{40}.
\end{align*}

What is the positive square root of the product $10 \times 15 \times 24$? ||| \begin{align*}
\sqrt{10 \cdot 15 \cdot 24} &= \sqrt{(10\cdot15) \cdot 24} \\
&= \sqrt{150 \cdot 24} \\
&= \sqrt{3600} \\
&= \boxed{60}.
\end{align*}

